content:
Configure the Home Page

Your template contains a standard Home page that is optional to configure.

REQUIRED EDITIONS AND USER PERMISSIONS
Available in: Lightning Experience, Enterprise, Performance, and Unlimited Editions with Customer Service Catalog add-on license.
Service Catalog site requires Service Catalog User permission set and a Channel Account, Customer Community, or Partner Community license.


USER PERMISSIONS NEEDED
Permissions and licenses associated with Aura Service Catalog Site Builder

Add the Service Catalog Grid component to display featured catalog items.
From Setup, enter All Sites, select All Sites, click Builder, Experience Builder opens, click , search for Service Catalog Grid, select it and configure properties.

Salesforce Help: Create a Catalog Item
Mark a Catalog Item as Featured
